data.description: Charming Colonial in the Heart of University Heights! CHECK OUT THE 360 DEGREE VIRTUAL TOUR!!! Spacious Light Filled Living Room w/ Gas Fireplace leads to the formal Dining Room. Updated Kitchen w/ Stainless Steel Appliances. First Floor Family room off of the Dining Room leads via Sliders to a raised private deck as well as the attached 2 car garage. Private fenced in backyard. Updated Half Bath on the 1st. Three Generously Sized Bedrooms along with an large updated bath w/ separate tub & shower. Partially finished lower level gives you that much more home to enjoy. Home Warranty Included. Call for your private showing Today!
